posting_body: ['Spacious Top Floor Apartment, 1 Car Garage, Fresh Paint, Wood Laminate Flooring!', 'Property Address', '5608 Hoffman Ct - 3 | San Jose, CA 95118', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Presidential Real Estate, Inc |', 'show contact info', 'Description', '5608 Hoffman Ct #3, San Jose, CA  95118  (Blossom Hill/Almaden)', 'Spacious top floor 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom apartment in a central San Jose location.', 'The home features an open floor plan with fresh paint, and wood laminate flooring.', 'The home has been updated with dual pane windows and the kitchen has white cabinets, and tile counters.', ' The bathroom includes white cabinets, a tile counter, tile flooring, and tiled shower enclosure.', '1 car shared garage plus 1 additional space.', 'Water and garbage is included in the rent.', 'One year lease required.', 'No pets except for required service animals.', 'Cal DRE# 01998337', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,350.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $2,000.00']
